<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><aka>&quot;I love thy kingdom, Lord.&quot;</aka>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Chisʋs an Chitokaka ma!
 Chim apehlichika
 Chim issish isht ish chumpa tok,
 Hulitobli lishke.

[V2]
 Chim apehlichika chin chʋch,
 Ilʋppak fehna hosh
 Hatak moma yukpalishke,
 Ai a̱hli fehnʋshke.

[V3]
 Chim apehlichika yokʋt
 Achukma fehnʋshke
 Sʋbbak, sa chu̱kʋsh aiena
 Isht ak chi apelá.

[V4]
 Chim apehlichika yoka
 Ak apelachokmʋt,
 Sʋbbak ʋt nan inla 'k heno
 Ik apelo kashke.

[V5]
 Nana inla yokak heno
 Ʋmi haksi pullʋt
 Sʋbbak, sʋtih aiena kʋt
 Kinnet iksho kashke.

[V6]
 Chim apehlichika yoka
 Apelahanchi hosh
 Toksahanlit, nishkin okchi
 A̱ kʋnihi̱ashke.

[V7]
 Toksʋli inla moma ka
 Ʋm i̱ shaiyahlashke;
 Ʋba isht asihi̱lhha li
 Bilia pullashke.</lyrics>
<title>Chisʋs an Chitokaka ma! ƲIT149</title>
<time_sig>C.M. (8.6.8.6.)</time_sig>
<author>Tune: &quot;I love thy kingdom, Lord.&quot;, Israel Folsom</author>
<hymn_number>149</hymn_number>
</song>